{"prompt": "Generate a website for a music streaming service. The brand color should be a lively yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Harmony Stream</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fef9e7; /* Light yellow background */\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #ffd700; /* Lively yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #fef9e7;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            background-color: #fef9e7; /* Light yellow background */\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #e6b400; /* Darker yellow for heading */\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            text-align: center;\n            max-width: 300px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        